skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: what a conundrum
des: What a Conundrum helps you get a conversation started by proposing two choices which you and your friends would choose between. There will come a time when using What a Conundrum where a topic comes up that spurs a heated discussion, so be sure to keep the fire extinguisher handy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
